{"tid":1008623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼貿易部長：穿二手衣會得愛滋病","createTime":"2019-02-04T15:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T03:35:46.000Z","uid":42188,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bdace836f6469874de5b092eb6dea564837ab295","tid":1008623,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T15:38:33.000Z","msg":"印尼貿易部長拉瑪特（Rachmat Gobel）遭國內家庭執行協會的董事長Winarso批評，竟為了印尼國內的紡織業，公開表示穿著外國進口的二手衣會得感染愛滋病和皮膚病，甚至信誓旦旦的說這是經過研究證實的。<br />\n<br />\n此言論一出，讓網友群起砲轟，雖然拉瑪特（Rachmat Gobel）在推特公開道歉，表示自己的本意是不想進口二手衣，以保護國內紡織業並預防疾病傳播，強調自己沒有惡意，但網友還是不領情。<br />\n<br />\n而Winarso認為拉瑪特（Rachmat Gobel）這樣的聲明在有許多人感染愛滋病的印尼，會讓其他人對愛滋病有更大的誤解，而造成更加嚴重的歧視。他希望政府在解決這個問題之前，可以先好好的了解愛滋病的傳播方式，不要再有人誤會了。"},{"pid":"2658e3e89b66b6508ff36a4fbfe936eca59fc8c3","tid":1008623,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T00:00:31.000Z","msg":"揭露真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揾人攪掂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 坐過基佬嘅凳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e48d883d5a72fbe0f6bb3d2e473201c851a528b","tid":1008623,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:14:54.000Z","msg":"我上次咪咁中 絕對無叫過雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763b02ea25b469798d69f0f546ba10dff082e923","tid":1008623,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e48d883d5a72fbe0f6bb3d2e473201c851a528b","tid":1008623,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:14:54.000Z","msg":"我上次咪咁中 絕對無叫過雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:28:47.000Z","msg":"係咪因爲你無交稅先中"},{"pid":"7ffe7912b268132648421cf000da56ae4fe77ba1","tid":1008623,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:31:08.000Z","msg":"到底係咪伊斯蘭國家多數無撚腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\